Wordcount.java: Mapreduce job(s) to count the total number of words in the file plot_summaries.txt. 
The output file should contain only one number: the total number of words.

WordFreq.java: Mapreduce job(s) to find 10 most frequent words in the plot-summaries dataset. 
The words should be ordered in descending order by their number of occurrences in the dataset.

WordFreqStop.java Do the same task of WordFreq, but excluding  those stop words in the stop.txt.

Join.java: Mapreduce job(s) to join the character.metadata.tsv and movie.metadata.tsv datasets and create a file, 
which has the following fields:
i. Wikipedia Movie ID
ii. Movie Name
iii, iv, v, â€¦ Actor Name (possibly) multiple

Index.java_ Mapreduce job(s) to create an inverted index for the plot-summaries dataset. 
The index should be a mapping from the term to the Wikipedia movie ID and the number of occurrences. 
For example, if the term "assignment" occurs 5 times in the plot summary of the movie whose Wikipedia movie ID is 42, 
then the index should contain a mapping from "assignment" to 42 and 5.
